                                                Energy
                                            
                                        </h4>
                                        <h3 class="eb-item__title">
                                            <a href="/news/china-responsible-for-95-of-new-coal-power-construction-in-2023-report-says/" class="eb-item__link">
                                                China responsible for 95% of new coal power construction in 2023, report says
                                            </a>
                                        </h3>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="eb-item__standfirst">
                                        
                                        
                                            China accounted for 95 per cent of the world’s new coal power construction activity in 2023, according to the latest annual report from Global Energy Monitor (GEM).
                                        
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <a href="/news/china-responsible-for-95-of-new-coal-power-construction-in-2023-report-says/" class="u-faux-block-link__overlay" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">China responsible for 95% of new coal power construction in 2023, report says</a>
