                                        </a>
                                    </h3>
                                </div>
                                <div class="eb-item__standfirst">
                                    
                                    
                                        Japan-based academic Kim Schumacher, who coined the term &quot;competence greenwashing&quot;, believes that the pursuit of societal harmony might be standing in the way of Asia calling out greenwashing. He tells the Eco-Business Podcast how exaggerated ESG claims are likely to be tackled in 2023 and beyond.
                                    
